WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.640 --> 00:00:03.900
Oozy -- an appetizer from Syria

00:00:04.980 --> 00:00:08.840
For the list of ingredients check the description box

00:00:13.680 --> 00:00:18.160
In a pan heat the olive oil, add the diced chicken, stir for about 4 minutes.

00:00:31.000 --> 00:00:35.660
Add the diced vegetables.

00:00:35.880 --> 00:00:38.720
Start by adding diced onions

00:00:43.620 --> 00:00:47.860
Add carrots, bell peppers and keep stirring.

00:00:48.320 --> 00:00:51.940
Add any other vegetables or your choice.

00:00:54.700 --> 00:00:58.200
Add salt/peppers and the 7 spices.

00:01:12.780 --> 00:01:16.180
Meanwhile cook rice

00:01:20.960 --> 00:01:24.120
Add rice to the vegetables mix and add some chopped parsley

00:01:24.380 --> 00:01:27.420
You can add some toasted pine nuts

00:01:27.420 --> 00:01:30.780
In a small bowl, line it with a piece of the puff pastry stretching it in all directions

00:01:33.160 --> 00:01:37.540
Fill with the previously prepared chicken mixture, and fold the sides up

00:01:40.560 --> 00:01:44.340
Carefully transfer it to an oven safe dish

00:01:50.780 --> 00:01:53.380
Brush with an egg beaten with a dash of black pepper

00:02:03.540 --> 00:02:08.860
Bake in a preheated oven of 350F until golden brown. Took me about 35 minutes.

00:02:25.920 --> 00:02:30.260
Serve with green salad or yogurt dip

00:02:31.120 --> 00:02:34.120
Enjoy !!

